comments: Niang (PHI) legally contests the jump shot attempt from Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) reaches in for the ball and his left shoulder makes contact with the face of Harden (PHI) during the drive.

Lopez (MIL) briefly places and removes a marginal hand from the right shoulder of Embiid (PHI) as he gathers into his shot. The marginal touch does not impact Emiid's shot attempt outside the painted area.
Middleton (MIL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Harden (PHI) and incidental contact occurs as the players come together.
Niang (PHI) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Holiday (MIL) and some marginal contact occurs that does not inhibit Holiday's defensive play.

Harden (PHI) gathers the ball and raises his arms out in front of him when some contact occurs with the right arm of Antetokounmpo (MIL); however, the latter collapses his arm as the distance closes and the marginal contact does not affect Harden's release near the rim.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: RLB shows Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes last contact with the ball before it careens out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to Philadelphia.
Harris (PHI) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and disengage while rebounding.
Harden's (PHI) off-arm comes out slightly during his change of direction but the contact to Holiday's (MIL) front is marginal.
Harris (PHI) briefly grasps and releases the jersey of Middleton (MIL) and there is no effect on the latter's FOM.
RLB shows Lopez (MIL) does not step out of bounds prior while in possession of the ball.
Holiday (MIL) moves his foot backwards and contact occurs between his foot and the ball that deflects the entry pass.
Holiday (MIL) and Harden (PHI) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal as Harden moves to set a pick for Embiid (PHI).
Lopez (MIL) places a hand to the midsection of Embiid (PHI) after the release of the shot and the marginal touch has no impact on Embiid's shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Millsap (PHI) extends his arms into Matthews (MIL) and dislodges him from his position during the rebound.
Harden (PHI) has his off-arm in the chest of Holiday (MIL) and retracts it during his reject of the on-ball screen. Holiday is not dislodged by the marginal contact.
Lopez (MIL) legally contests the perimeter shot attempt by Harden (PHI).

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of defensive goaltending by Antetokounmpo (MIL) is overturned to a clean block.  The ball is loose at the time of the whistle and therefore, there is a jump ball when play resumes.
Middleton (MIL) brings his right forearm to the side of Embiid (PHI) and the marginal body contact does not impact the shot attempt near the rim.
